item.title: TryHackMe - DAV Writeup
item.author: SHAFIQAIMAN
item.description: Link : https://tryhackme.com/room/bsidesgtdav Enumeration First we need to connect to try hack me networks through openvpn and deploy the machine. Now, the box is up. So, first we need to do a reconnaissance using nmap. Nmap is a network mapper tools for scanning the ports or enumerate the machine through ports. I will run this command for my nmap scan. 1 nmap -sC -sV -oN nmap/initial <machine ip> Explaining the nmap flag: -sC := scan using nmap default script -sV := scan for version -oN := output in normal format The result of our nmap scan
